This is a polling module for BrowerCMS.

Bugs:
====
* Users cannot add additional questions, even though the UI appears to support it. Add Responses aren't saved.
* Blank answers cause data to be lost.
* Responses cannot be deleted either.
* When a user votes, the page says 'Back to Poll'. Rather than 'Reset Poll'.

Minor Issues
=====
* Tab order for responses is wrong.
